T_f
\phi_{n}\to\phi
T_{f}(\phi_n)\to T_f(\phi)
T_{f}(\phi)\le ||\phi||_{\infty}\int_{K}|f(x)|dx
\phi_n \to \phi
\mathcal{D}
K
\text{supp} \phi_n \subseteq K
n \in \mathbb{N}
\|\phi_n-\phi\|_{\infty} \to 0 \qquad (n \to \infty)
|T_f(\phi_n)-T_f(\phi)| =|T_f(\phi_n-\phi)| \leq \|\phi_n-\phi\|_{\infty} \cdot \int_K |f(x)| \, dx \to 0 \qquad (n \to \infty)
